rows.label: tlk70000080_10_msg0002
rows.name:
I was pretty far back in the crowd
while you were being knighted, but I
still saw the ceremony.

rows.label: tlk70000080_10_msg0003
rows.name:
There hasn't been a Driver who could
control the Paragon of Iira for a long
time now...

rows.label: tlk70000080_10_msg0004
rows.name:
We're so lucky to have you, Laura-sama.
And you too Shin

rows.label: tlk70000080_10_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm working as hard as I can to help
you defeat the Holy Grail. Let me know if
there's ever anything I can do.
